                fileSize: 3994008,
                releaseDate: "2026-05-31",
                isDefault: false,
                isPreRelease: false,
                changelog: ["**Added initial support for FW 8.x, 9.x, 10.x, 11.x, 12.x and 13.x.** \u26a0\ufe0f These are *initial support - testing required* (not yet hardware-validated). Feedback from users on these firmwares is welcome.", "**FW 6.x and 7.61 are hardware-validated.**", "Previously these firmwares failed to install (`SceShellCore not found`) and, even when forced, showed **blank process names** and **truncated memory maps**. All fixed:", "Install now succeeds.", "`PROC_INFO` / `PROC_LIST` show correct process names.", "`PROC_MAPS` returns the complete memory map.", "**Firmware-agnostic process lookup** - the installer now locates the target via a stable system call instead of per-firmware kernel offsets, making install more robust across firmwares.", "**Kernel-patch guard** - the installer now detects when the jailbreak has *already* applied the kernel patch and skips re-writing it, **preventing a kernel panic** seen on 7.61.", "**Corrected per-firmware process-info offsets** - process name / path / title ID / content ID now read correctly on 6.x and newer (were frozen at 4.x values and came back empty on 6.x+).", "Added **EchoStretch** and **Sonic-Iso** to the special thanks."]
